# Netcoins
# Blockchain and Cryptocurrencies Company in Canada

## Overview and Origin

### Name of Company
* NetCoins is the Canadian Fintech company I have chosen for assignment #1.

### When was Netcoins incorporated?
* Netcoins was incoporated on 2014-07-08 in the Province of British Columbia. 
* Netcoins registered with The Financial Transactions and Reports Analysis Centre of Canada (FINTRAC) Money Services Business (MSB) Registry on 2015-05-18. 
* MSB Registration Number M15560893
* Incorporation # BC1007550
https://www10.fintrac-canafe.gc.ca/msb-esm/public/detailed-information/msb-details/7b226d73624f72674e756d626572223a3134323136392c227072696d617279536561726368223a7b226f72674e616d65223a226e6574636f696e73222c2273656172636854797065223a317d7d/


### Who are the founders of the company?

* The founders of Netcoins are Michael Vogel and Dominic Vogel.
https://www.vancouverisawesome.com/courier-archive/news/turned-down-by-dragons-den-netcoins-hits-the-stock-exchange-3070567#:~:text=1%20%2F%202%20Dominic%20(left),the%20Dragon's%20Den%20in%202016.

* Netcoin is owned by BIGG Digital Assets.
https://netcoins.ca/investors/

### How did the idea for the company (or project) come about?

* The idea for Netcoins grew out of th idea for a Bitcoin ATM and actulally grew out an accelerator program offered by TriCelerate in Coquitlam British Columbia.
https://www.vancouverisawesome.com/courier-archive/news/turned-down-by-dragons-den-netcoins-hits-the-stock-exchange-3070567#:~:text=1%20%2F%202%20Dominic%20(left),the%20Dragon's%20Den%20in%202016.

### How is the company funded? How much funding have they received?

* Netcoins is ultimately funded by its users which totaled +80,000 users with 19,000 active users in Quarter 2 of 2021. Quarter 2 revenues in 2021 reached $4.2 million.
https://financialpost.com/globe-newswire/bigg-digital-assets-inc-announces-record-quarterly-revenue-at-cad-4-6-million-and-880-year-over-year-growth#:~:text=Netcoins%20revenue%20was%20~%244.2,Registered%20users%20now%20exceeds%2080%2C000

* Commissions are earned based on a flat trading fee of 0.50% as well as a withdrawal fee of 0.50% when cashin out Crypto to a fiat currency or moving to another platform. 
Deposits to a crypto wallet and fiat currency wallets are free. 
Withdrawals from a fiat currency wallet to another financial institutoin are also free.
https://www.savvynewcanadians.com/netcoins-review/  

